<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694246>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Male genitalia of Siberian Ennominae.A, B—Glacies sajana; C, D—G.coracina; E, F—Charissa(Kemtrognophos) remmi; G, H—Ch. (K.) ambiguata; I–O—Ch. (Dysgnophos) turfosaria. A, C, E, G, I—genital segment; B, D, F, H, J–O—phallos. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4694246/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694294>
    dc:description "FIGURE 34. Female genitalia of Siberian Ennominae.A—Ourapteryx ussurica; B—Hylaea fasciaria; C—Perconia strigillaria; D—Yezognophos vittaria; E—Glacies sajana; F—G. coracina; G—Charissa (Kemtrognophos) remmi; H—Ch. (K.) ambiguata. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4694294/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

